title: Executive Proposal - “Update the wBTC and USDC Debt Ceilings”
body:
If the Mimo Token Holders accept this executive proposal, the following changes will be deployed to the Mimo Protocol:

- The wBTC debt ceiling will be decreased from 10 million PAR to 6 million PAR
- The USDC debt ceiling will be decreased from 10 million PAR to 4 million PAR

**BE INFORMED**
Please make sure to inform and educate yourself before proceeding with your vote. Community discussions are always welcomed.
author: 0xaC3203D77823496E421aA7E88CDC2F6C387d6182
